Book Examples for Dialogs
Chapter 11

ch11_dialogs

DialogExample

	Project DialogExample contains a single top component with buttons 
	to show the various dialog types discussed in the chapter.

	The project includes a Login Dialog that appears right 
	after the NetBeans Platform splash screen. 

	To successfully login, make the username and password the same!

RoleExample

	Project RoleExample is the sample project for the section 
	'Putting It All Together'.

	For the Login dialog, use 

	Meg for username and Meg for password (this is role "Admin") or 
	Joe for username and Joe for password (this is role "User").

	Use the same values for Menu/Tools - Change Role action.